%I A393702 #52 Jun 28 2026 19:44:48
%S A393702 0,0,6,6,169,469,3615,3681,114621,257690
%N A393702 First number to occur at least n times in Weinstein's W sequence (A394611).
%C A393702 Presumed infinite, but there is currently no proof.
%e A393702 The first term of A394611 is 0, so 0 is the first number to occur once, a(1)=0.
%e A393702 The second term of A394611 is also 0, so 0 is the first number to occur twice, a(2)=0.
%e A393702 When we reach term 10 of A394611, the number 6 becomes the first number to appear 3 times, so a(3)=6.
%Y A393702 Cf. A394611, A397175.
%K A393702 nonn,new
%O A393702 1,3
%A A393702 _Sean A. Irvine_, Jun 28 2026
